data.description: Cute, Updated, Move in Ready, Concrete Block 2 bedroom 1 bath home close to shopping, the avenues and easy access to 95 and the beaches!   Open floor plan with vinyl and carpet. Shaker kitchen cabs with granite countertops. City Water and sewer and fenced yard.  Large Patio for entertaining and carport.
